descript.abstract: This data layer represents land use for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Adams_LandUse_2010.gdb.
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for students, faculty, and staff of the University of Wisconsin-Madison for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
descript.supplinf: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable.
